# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok soldiers enforced a curfew in this west bank town monday after palestinian gunmen fired at a commuter bus , killing two jewish settlers and wounding five .
# ::alignments
(e / enforce-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (s / soldier)))
      :ARG1 (c / curfew)
      :location (t / town
            :location (c2 / country-region
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "West"
                        :op2 "Bank"))
            :mod (t2 / this))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (f / fire-01
                  :ARG0 (g / gunman
                        :mod (c3 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Palestine")))
                  :destination (b / bus
                        :mod (c4 / commute-01))
                  :ARG0-of (k / kill-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :quant 2
                              :ARG1-of (s2 / settle-03)
                              :mod (r / religious-group
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Jew"))))
                  :ARG0-of (w / wound-01
                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :quant 5)))))

                        :op2 "Yahoo"))
            :mod (ii / internet))
      :ARG1 (e / email-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1-of (a / alert-01
                  :ARG2 (c3 / change-01
                        :ARG1 (c4 / contract
                              :poss c)
                        :ARG2-of (ii2 / include-01
                              :ARG1 (a2 / and
                                    :op1 (ii3 / issue-02
                                          :ARG1-of (l / legal-02))
                                    :op2 (ii4 / issue-02
                                          :ARG1-of l))))))
      :time (w / week
            :mod (t / this)))

                                                :op1 "Egypt"))
                                    :ARG2 (p3 / president))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :accompanier (d2 / decide-01
            :ARG0 (o2 / organization
                  :name (n4 / name

                        :mod c)
                  :ARG2 (s3 / state
                        :ARG0-of h2

                                    :op2 "Nations"))
                        :ARG2 (m / member)))
            :ARG1-of (e / expect-01
                  :time (w / week
                        :mod (n6 / next)))))

                  :ARG1 p)))
